## When to Update

Update the `Last Updated` or `Updated` field when:
- Making substantive changes to the file
- Fixing bugs
- Adding new functionality
- Refactoring code

**Do NOT update** for:
- Minor whitespace changes
- Automated formatting
- Comment-only changes

---

## Verification Checklist

Before committing:
- [ ] New files have authorship header/footer
- [ ] Modified files have updated date (if substantive changes)
- [ ] Date format is consistent (YYYY-MM-DD)
- [ ] Author attribution is correct

